## Query Key Factory

```typescript
// lib/constants/query-keys.constant.ts
export const queryKeys = {
  chat: {
    sessions: ["chat", "sessions"] as const,
    session: (id: string) => ["chat", "session", id] as const,
    messages: (sessionId: string) => ["chat", "messages", sessionId] as const,
  },
  review: {
    all: ["reviews"] as const,
    byUser: (userId: string) => ["reviews", userId] as const,
  },
  knowledge: {
    all: ["knowledge"] as const,
  },
} as const;
```

---

## Rules Summary

- ✅ Server Actions call Supabase directly — no external API
- ✅ Always check auth inside Server Actions
- ✅ Custom hook wraps every mutation — never raw `useMutation` in components
- ✅ Centralize query keys
- ❌ Never use Axios or external fetch in Server Actions
